// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0474 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f882416f-2f45-5c23-a764-0bed2f10ba33

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
